    "896, 2023-2024 Reg.",
    "(Cal. 2024).",
    "256 Council Regulation 2024/1689, Laying Down Harmonised Rules on Artificial Intelligence, 2024 O.J.",
    "59:601 Public Constitutional AI framework.",
    "257 This could create a powerful incentive for companies to invest in Public Constitutional AI compliance, as it would provide them with a degree of legal protection against potential harms or violations caused by their AI systems."
